title: Free Car Seat Safety Check Event in Calais (Maine Families of Washington County)
text: ( Source : Maine Families of Washington County ) Did you know that 3 out of 4 child car seats are used incorrectly? Join us at Calais Regional Hospital 's Health & Wellness Fair on October 27th for a free child car seat check. Nicole , a
